Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTA----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然挡住了我们四人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样同化他们的星核
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 D岛的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要为哥哥报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队 距离20
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强足够引擎重新启动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不动就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎维持原状 放出机械鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告人类军战士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我们正在执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让新来的星核对人类有所助益
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们愿意向诸位提供所获得的所有数据
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队展开 要被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在表明选择对话的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择对话？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到大量联络
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是太平洋舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这令人难以置信的大量数据是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是波利尼西亚舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告知 那边有Festum吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fs34}真壁…是指那个真壁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们都被骗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相到底是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的声音…传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道会变成这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们抛弃了新联合国这个大义名分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要统管大军为时尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的核操纵人心的手段也有限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令执行交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗分子全部肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:01:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操控权被夺取了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与敌人的共存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「三重计划」所埋葬的就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机 切换为常规炮弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标变更
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军…在帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整波长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要归还希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为弟弟对星核许愿才能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你祈求了弓子的生命一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…妈妈还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈还好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 你不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁…由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里尔 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是人 但是能感觉到心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别犹豫 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来消除你与星核的调和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现我们的希望…光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里尔 执行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都给我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈班闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿输柯？怎么复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用虫洞侵入这护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复生太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那机体的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 变成我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛的星核在守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝他 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上岛会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于能理解你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解你的力量有多伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己吧 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和爸爸 都会一直陪伴在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真庆幸能遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最好的朋友 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将与这座岛的星核一起循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再好好聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漫长的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我将归还这生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屹立于世吧 吾等之希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里尔 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为哥哥报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里尔 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里尔程序 强制终止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里尔 执行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单机的攻击无法破坏护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那怪物抹消掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个就是你 真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来弑杀世界的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 Mk.Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还未到终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置更新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有你能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阻止流浪者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来感觉真是爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让同伴来指挥 只管去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽也很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够诞生于世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 同化我们的憎恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何去了那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到我的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵牛星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹的星核来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等的力量 大家都受其支配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西…要怎么对付啊
