Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知星核从上空接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 伴随着你们离岛的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽在将我的声音传达给那个星核
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让它沉眠在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要转变成有益的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做到这点力量还太幼小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要同化你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连憎恨的理由都忘却的绝望之核
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在与虚无的力量将阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核的亡灵啊 能感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:11:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赐予你们的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达了最充满希望的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后终有一天 再让岛觉醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将生命归还给岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接下一个诞生的核吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令执行D计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行D计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立上 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要犹豫 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直视未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐战斗将我们守护到底的岛之核
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城织姬 感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家的祈愿 我才得以诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALVIS全员 一定会回归这个岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄美？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来推行计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰上充满岛的空气 会让你存活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不长久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 至少让我留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你沉睡之前 我会保持通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你能够说出道别的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有了你这个拥有人心的核
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才能存活至今
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使消失 也会在某处留下存在的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 翔子 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心现在在哪里 光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…杀了艾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我抹消吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 快离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬 你总是一个人哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使悲伤也守护着大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会守护织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 小芹要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有力量改变你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 可以让你沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球上 能和你对话的人在未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请沉睡到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两舰出航进程开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛进入了自动潜航模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要长官在CDC里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 快离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去吧 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和剑司一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 妈妈 妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就过去 诚一郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也睡吧 直到岛觉醒的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期 小芹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全岛民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是灭亡 是新的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终有一天 定将重归故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…最终到达的未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗 Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在消失的恐惧 就是痛楚的根源吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对诞生的恐惧也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦 悲伤…生存的一切都是祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:18:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接纳所有 祝福世界之时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都将开创充满希望的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时 你都可以相信这未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了吗 织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也回去吧 回归生命之源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festum的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是其入口 存在与虚无的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次终将跨越地平线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将虚无与存在的调和 交托给未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋 来主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导大家前往未来吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 在彼此的祝福彼方再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥总是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾和光弘也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我却不知道什么是正确的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽 姐姐她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你守护了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:22:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回我们的岛去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 那对面有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界 和你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…故乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终将知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是充满痛苦的生 也要选择存在的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将使我们相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随着世界的祝福 我们将不断邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断回归仍未得见的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论几度
